VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT yaml\.load\((?!.*Loader=yaml\.FullLoader)(.*?)\)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:yaml\.safe_load|Loader=yaml\.SafeLoader
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the usage of yaml.load without specifying the Loader as yaml.FullLoader, which may lead to potential security risks.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for YAML Loading: Use safe_load.
